# Global Liquidity Dashboard — Design Document

> **Purpose:** Pass this document to Cursor (or any AI coding assistant) to implement a fully working, self-updating web dashboard that visualises global central bank liquidity alongside S&P 500, Nasdaq, and Bitcoin.

---

## 1. Project Overview

A single-page web application (vanilla HTML/CSS/JS or React — see Tech Stack) that displays:

1. **Global Liquidity Chart** — combined central bank balance sheets / M2 aggregates, with toggleable breakdown by country
2. **US Liquidity Chart** — dedicated US view with Fed balance sheet + M2
3. **Australia Liquidity Chart** — RBA-related data via FRED
4. **Asset Overlay** — toggle S&P 500, Nasdaq 100, and Bitcoin onto any chart
5. **Auto-refresh** — data refreshes weekly, with a visible "Last Updated" badge

