## 3. Data Sources & APIs

### 3.1 FRED API (Federal Reserve Economic Data)
- **Provider:** St. Louis Federal Reserve — free, reliable, well-documented
- **Base URL:** `https://api.stlouisfed.org/fred/series/observations`
- **Auth:** Free API key from https://fred.stlouisfed.org/docs/api/api_key.html
- **Format:** JSON

**Series to fetch:**

| Series ID | Description | Frequency | Unit |
|---|---|---|---|
| `WALCL` | US Fed Balance Sheet (Total Assets) | Weekly | USD Millions |
| `M2SL` | US M2 Money Supply | Monthly | USD Billions |
| `ECBASSETSW` | ECB Total Assets | Weekly | EUR Millions |
| `JPNASSETS` | Bank of Japan Total Assets | Monthly | JPY Billions |
| `MYAGM2CNM189N` | China M2 Money Supply | Monthly | CNY Billions |
| `MYAGM2AUM189N` | Australia M2 Money Supply | Monthly | AUD Millions |
| `DEXUSEU` | USD/EUR Exchange Rate | Daily | Rate |
| `DEXJPUS` | JPY/USD Exchange Rate | Daily | Rate |
| `DEXCHUS` | CNY/USD Exchange Rate | Daily | Rate |
| `DEXUSAL` | USD/AUD Exchange Rate | Daily | Rate |

> **Currency Conversion Note:** All non-USD series must be converted to USD for the global chart. Fetch the most recent exchange rates from FRED and multiply. See Section 6 for implementation detail.

### 3.2 CoinGecko API (Bitcoin)
- **Base URL:** `https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/coins/bitcoin/market_chart`
- **Auth:** Free tier — no key required (rate limited to ~30 req/min)
- **Endpoint:** `GET /coins/bitcoin/market_chart?vs_currency=usd&days=1825&interval=weekly`
- **Returns:** Array of `[timestamp, price]` pairs

### 3.3 Yahoo Finance (via AllOrigins proxy — no API key needed)
Yahoo Finance doesn't have an official API, but its chart endpoint is publicly accessible. Use a CORS proxy:

```
https://query1.finance.yahoo.com/v8/finance/chart/{SYMBOL}?interval=1wk&range=5y
```

Symbols:
- S&P 500: `^GSPC`
- Nasdaq 100: `^NDX`

**CORS Workaround:** Use `https://api.allorigins.win/get?url=` as a prefix, or implement a tiny Cloudflare Worker as a proxy (Cursor can scaffold this).

> **Alternative:** If Yahoo Finance is unreliable, use **Alpha Vantage** (free tier, API key required): `https://www.alphavantage.co/query?function=TIME_SERIES_WEEKLY&symbol=SPY`

