## 5. Smart Release-Aware Refresh Logic

Rather than a naive 7-day timer, the dashboard should understand the release calendar and only fetch when new data is actually available. This is how Bloomberg terminals and economic data platforms behave.

### Core concept: per-series "next expected release" date

Each cached series stores:
```js
{
  seriesId: "WALCL",
  data: [...],
  lastDataPointDate: "2025-04-10",   // Date of most recent observation
  fetchedAt: 1744300000000,          // Unix ms when we last fetched
  nextExpectedRelease: 1744671000000 // Unix ms of next scheduled release
}
```

### Release schedule calculator

```js
