## 9. Key Implementation Notes for Cursor

### 8.1 Aligning Time Series
FRED data returns different frequencies (weekly vs monthly). Normalise everything to **monthly** by:
1. Downsampling weekly data to end-of-month values
2. Forward-filling gaps in monthly series for display purposes

```js
// Pseudocode
function toMonthly(observations) {
  const monthly = {};
  for (const obs of observations) {
    const key = obs.date.slice(0, 7); // "YYYY-MM"
    monthly[key] = obs.value; // Last value in month wins
  }
  return monthly;
}
```

### 8.2 Global Liquidity Calculation
```js
// Convert each country's central bank assets to USD, then sum
globalLiquidity[date] =
  usFed_USD[date] +
  ecb_EUR[date] * usdPerEur[date] +
  boj_JPY[date] / jpyPerUsd[date] +
  pboc_CNY[date] / cnyPerUsd[date];
```

